Titolo: Metal Knight

Anno: 1998

Descrizione: Metal Knight (Chinese: 铁甲风暴; lit. 'Ironclad Storm') is a sci-fi type real-time strategy released in 1998, developed by Object Software Limited and published in mainland China by Object Software and in Taiwan by T-time Technology Co., Ltd. In 1999 the English version was published by Microforum in the USA and Italy. The game supports eight online players. The game sold over 300,000 copies and received high ratings from indigenous game magazines such as Popsoft and Play. There is an expansion named Black Front.